Package com.vector.cfg.consistency.groovy.api

This package contains interfaces and classes for an automation client to interact with the consistency component.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IResultFilterSolvingActionMapperBuilder
    This builder interface is used to specify which validation results should by solved with which solving action.
    ISolver
    This interface is used to solve multiple results within one transaction.
    ISolvingActionSelect
    This interface is used to select a solving action within a validation result.
    See documentation of the complete fluent API in ISolver.solve(Closure).
    IValidationApi
    The main interface for validation.
    IValidationApiEntryPoint
    Methods of this interface are callable in every code block with an active project in context.
    IValidationResultCreationApi
    The IValidationResultCreationApi provides methods to create new IValidationResult instances via the IValidationResultBuilder to add validation-results e.g during generation.
    IValidationResultForSolvingActionSelect
    A specialized interface of a validation-result for selecting one solving-action.

Package com.vector.cfg.consistency.groovy.api Description

This package contains interfaces and classes for an automation client to interact with the consistency component.
